OL,3,CVulnerable residents asked to pay more
OL,4,Cfor medical waste disposal
OL,6,FSome vulnerable adults in Guernsey may
OL,7,Fneed to pay more for disposing of
OL,8,Fessential medical waste after the
OL,9,Fisland's Adult Community Services
OL,10,Fstopped providing yellow waste bags.
OL,12,FThe changes mean that medical waste
OL,13,Fwill now need to be disposed of in
OL,14,Fblack bin bags, which is a chargeable
OL,15,Fservice in Guernsey.
OL,17,FYellow clinical waste bags are used
OL,18,Ffor incontinence waste, feminine
OL,19,Fhygiene products, stoma and catheter
OL,20,Fproducts, used but uncontaminated
OL,21,Fgloves and aprons.
