OL,3,CVulnerable residents asked to pay more
OL,4,Cfor medical waste disposal
OL,6,FIn a letter from the Guernsey States-
OL,7,Frun Adult Community Services, tenants
OL,8,Fin extra care housing facilities were
OL,9,Fadvised that work has started to build
OL,10,Fa new combined animal and clinical
OL,11,Fwaste incinerator at Longue Hougue
OL,12,Fwaste management site, which is
OL,13,Fexpected to finish in 2026.
OL,15,FUntil the new incinerator is
OL,16,Foperational, medical waste that used
OL,17,Fto be taken away for free will have to
OL,18,Fbe paid for.
