OL,3,CVulnerable residents asked to pay more
OL,4,Cfor medical waste disposal
OL,6,FThe letter to tenants continues: "We
OL,7,Fare being asked to review how we
OL,8,Fmanage waste across Health and Social
OL,9,FCare including Extra Care Housing and
OL,10,Fensure that we are reducing the amount
OL,11,Fof waste that is being incinerated.
OL,13,F"Currently several items of waste are
OL,14,Fbeing disposed of in yellow bags which
OL,15,Fis classed as offensive waste and
OL,16,Fshould be placed in black domestic
OL,17,Fwaste bags".
