OL,3,CVulnerable residents asked to pay more
OL,4,Cfor medical waste disposal
OL,6,FThe Adult Community Services added
OL,7,Fthat it was "reviewing the need for
OL,8,Fclinical waste in communal areas and
OL,9,Findividual flats" and will no longer
OL,10,Fprovide yellow bags.
OL,12,FThese changes came into force at the
OL,13,Fstart of this year and will impact
OL,14,Fvulnerable people living in supported
OL,15,Fliving facilities.
OL,17,FMany of these residents have complex
OL,18,Fmedical needs and need to dispose of
OL,19,Fitems such as stoma products and
OL,20,Fincontinence waste.
