OL,3,CVulnerable residents asked to pay more
OL,4,Cfor medical waste disposal
OL,6,FThe change has concerned some in the
OL,7,Fcare industry, with one individual
OL,8,Ftelling ITV News that the changes will
OL,9,Fnow cost individual residents a huge
OL,10,Fsum as the black sacks are priced by
OL,11,Fweight.
OL,13,FA "Pay As You Throw" system operates
OL,14,Fin Guernsey, where households apply
OL,15,Fcoloured stickers to general household
OL,16,Fwaste depending on the size of the bin
OL,17,Fbag. This policy means that those who
OL,18,Fproduce the most waste pay the most.
