OL,6,FAs of 2026, the price of stickers has
OL,7,Fincreased, with a green sticker for a
OL,8,F90 litre black bin rising by 29 pence
OL,9,Ffrom #3.38 to #3.67, and an orange
OL,10,Fsticker for 50 litres going up by 16
OL,11,Fpence from #1.88 to #2.04.
